john w snow  wikipedia john w snow from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search not to be confused with jon snow character john w snow rd united states secretary of the treasury in office february   – june   president george w bush preceded by paul oneill succeeded by henry paulson personal details born john william snow  august   age  toledo ohio political party republican alma mater kenyon college university of toledo ba university of virginia phd george washington university law school jd signature john william snow born august   is the former ceo of csx corporation and served as the rd united states secretary of the treasury under us president george w bush he replaced secretary paul oneill on february   and was succeeded by henry paulson on july   in a move that had been anticipated snow submitted a letter of resignation on may   effective after an orderly transition period for my successor snow announced on june   that he had completed his last day on the job robert kimmitt served as acting secretary until paulson was sworn in snow is currently the chairman of cerberus capital management contents  background  public service during the nixonford period  career in the railway industry  public service during time in the private sector  further affiliations  secretary of the treasury  current positions  references  external links backgroundedit snow was born in toledo ohio the son of catherine howard a school teacher and william dean snow a tax attorney snow attended high school at gilmour academy in gates mills ohio he did his undergraduate studies at kenyon college where he was a member of the delta tau delta fraternity and the university of toledo from which he received a ba in  he received a phd in economics from the university of virginia in  from  to  he was an assistant professor of economics at the university of maryland he completed a juris doctor at the george washington university law school in  and then worked at the washington dc law firm of wheeler  wheeler from  to  snow lives in richmond virginia with his wife carolyn he has three children and six grandchildren snows alma mater kenyon college awarded him an honorary lld in  he has also received the us department of transportation secretarys outstanding achievement award and has been named a distinguished fellow by the yale school of management public service during the nixonford periodedit this section of a biography of a living person does not include any references or sources please help by adding reliable sources contentious material about living people that is unsourced or poorly sourced must be removed immediately find sources john w snow – news · newspapers · books · scholar · jstor october  learn how and when to remove this template message in  snow left wheeler  wheeler and took up a position as assistant professor of law at the george washington university law school during the three years he spent with the gwu law school snow also held positions in the us government in – as assistant general counsel for the department of transportation in – as deputy assistant secretary for policy plans and international affairs and in – as assistant secretary for governmental affairs in the department of transportation in  snow left gwu law school and took up the fulltime position of deputy undersecretary in the department of transportation in  he left this post when he was named as administrator of the national highway traffic safety administration with the election of jimmy carter snow departed public life in  during his transition period out of public life in spring  he served as a visiting professor of economics at the university of virginia and as a visiting fellow at the american enterprise institute in addition he was named a distinguished fellow at the yale school of management from  until  career in the railway industryedit snows years with the department of transportation proved useful to him as in  he became the vice president in charge of governmental affairs for chessie system inc a holding company that owned three american railroads the chesapeake and ohio railway aka the co for which the chessie system was named the western maryland railway and the baltimore and ohio railroad the bo of monopoly fame in  chessie system merged with another railroad holding company seaboard coast line industries to form csx corporation and snow became csxs senior vice presidentcorporate services at their new headquarters in richmond virginia in  he was promoted to executive vice president in  csx installed snow as president and ceo of their bo railroad and he oversaw its merger with their co railway in  this created a new entity csx transportation headquartered in jacksonville florida snow became the president and ceo of csx transportation in  snow left csx transportation the railroad to become president and chief operating officer of csx corporation the holding company as of april  he was president and chief executive officer of csx from  he also served as csxs chairman he continued to hold all three posts until he was named secretary of the treasury in  during snows tenure at csx deferred maintenance of the railroads physical plant became prevalent this is a common practice used by railroads to improve the bottom line for investors while the tracks themselves fall into disrepair miles of mainline were subjected to slow orders as a result increasing the need for more locomotives and rail cars and thus costing the company more money csx was forced to lease hundreds of locomotives to make up the difference further adding to the increased costs this practice ended with snows successor michael ward part of csx csx lines was sold to the carlyle group early in  after snow left the company for the white house csx sold its international port operations to the uae company dubai transport public service during time in the private sectoredit during ronald reagans campaign for the presidency in  snow was a member of governor reagans fourman advisory group on regulatory policy following his election victory presidentelect reagan named snow as vice chairman of his transportation transition team snow would go on to serve on the white house conference for a drug free america the services policy advisory committee of the us trade representative as cochair of the national commission on financial institution reform recovery and enforcement the national commission on intermodal transportation the national commission on economic growth and tax reform as a trustee of the virginia museum of fine arts and as a member of the richmond city school board he was the cochairman of the conference boards blueribbon commission on public trust and private enterprise he also served as cochairman of the national commission on financial institution reform recovery and enforcement in  that made recommendations following the savings and loan crisis from  through  he was chairman of the business roundtable a business policy group of  chief executive officers of the nations largest companies and played a major role in supporting passage of the north american free trade agreement further affiliationsedit snow has served as a director for bassett furniture industries inc circuit city stores inc nationsbank corp textron inc usx corporation the usjapan business council verizon communications and the association of american railroads snow was the founding chairman of the center for energy and economic development ceed a coal and rail industryfunded advocacy organization ceed was a predecessor organization to the american coalition for clean coal electricity accce he has served on the board of trustees of the johns hopkins university and the university of virginia darden school foundation he has been a member of the business roundtable the executive committee of the business council the virginia business council and the national coal council on october   snow was named chairman of cerberus capital management on august   snow was appointed the inaugural newman visiting fellow at the miller center of public affairs at the university of virginia he joined the board of directors of marathon petroleum corporation in  when that company was spun off from marathon oil corporation since  snow has been an avid supporter of israel as he stated on charleston south carolinas good morning charleston television programcitation needed john w snow at the  imfworld bank annual meeting secretary of the treasuryedit snow was nominated as secretary of the treasury by president george w bush on january   and unanimously confirmed by the us senate in july and august  snow and his colleagues labor secretary elaine chao and commerce secretary donald evans took a bus across the country on their jobs and growth tour aimed at promoting the benefits of the bush administrations tax cuts in january  the washington post quoted a senior administration official as saying that mr snow could stay as long as he wants provided its not very long in may  it was revealed that snows brokers had bought  million of debt issued by fannie mae and freddie mac on the day and day after snow was sworn into office as treasury secretary snow claimed this was done without his knowledge in february  when snow found out he divested the debt holdings a treasury ethics lawyer has found that the holdings did not represent a conflict of interest but had the potential to do so in the future on may   snow announced that he would resign effective july  he said the white house would make an official statement the following week on may  it was formally announced that snow would leave this position on this same day it was announced that president george w bush had nominated henry paulson ceo of goldman sachs to replace snow snow was forced to resign when it was uncovered that snow failed to pay income taxes on the  million of loan forgiveness he received while ceo of csx corporation bush stated publicly that he wanted a “new face” to head the treasury dept even though the stock market grew  during snow’s tenure as secretary current positionsedit in  snow joined fosun international of china as advisor to the board of directorscitation needed actually belongs to the iag international consolidated airlines group sa board iag is the result of iberia líneas aéreas de españa sa and british airways plc merger in april  he was one of eight former treasury secretaries who called on the united kingdom to remain a member of the european union ahead of the june  referendum referencesedit  inside report by robert novak – local news – news  lincoln tribune  instant reliable and credible local news  snow mulling leaving treasury post report – marketwatch  spend spend spend the bountiful economics of a president in denial – gerard baker – times online the times   monstersandcriticscomdead link  httpwwwcerberuscapitalcomteamjohnwsnow  httpwwwtoledobladecomlocalcerberuschairmanisexchiefoftreasurytoledonativehtml    johnston david cay free lunch how the wealthiest americans enrich themselves at government expense and stick you with the bill penguin books  pages –  httpwwwmarathonpetroleumcomaboutmpccorporateprofileboardofdirectorsjohnwsnow  bush economic team hits the road to promote tax cuts kentucky new era  retrieved    nytimescom  washingtonpostcom  vieth warren simon richard december   csx paid no income tax in  of the last  years los angeles times archived from the original on march    scroll down to third item on page article archived by archiveorg  bush george w decision points  staying in eu best hope for uks future say exus treasury secretaries bbc news april    external linksedit white house biography treasury department biography appearances on cspan political offices preceded by paul oneill us secretary of the treasury served under george w bush – succeeded by henry paulson v t e united states secretaries of the treasury th century hamilton wolcott dexter th century gallatin campbell dallas crawford rush ingha