ia phd george washington university law school jd signature john william snow born august   is the former ceo of csx corporation and served as the rd united states secretary of the treasury under us president george w bush he replaced secretary paul oneill on february   and was succeeded by henry paulson on july   in a move that had been anticipated snow submitted a letter of resignation on may   effective after an orderly transition period for my successor snow announced on june   that he had completed his last day on the job robert kimmitt served as acting secretary until paulson was sworn in snow is currently the chairman of cerberus capital management contents  background  public service during the nixonford period  career in the railway industry  public service during time in the private sector  further affiliations  secretary of the treasury  current positions  references  external links backgroundedit snow was born in toledo ohio the son of catherine howard a school teacher and william dean snow a tax attorney snow attended high school at gilmour academy in gates mills ohio he did his undergraduate studies at kenyon college where he was a member of the delta tau delta fraternity and the university of toledo from which he received a ba in  he received a phd in economics from the university of virginia in  from  to  he was an assistant professor of economics at the university of maryland he completed a juris doctor at the george washington university law school in  and then worked at the washington dc law firm of wheeler  wheeler from  to  snow lives in richmond virginia with his wife carolyn he has three children and six grandchildren snows alma mater kenyon college awarded him an honorary lld in  he has also received the us department of transportation secretarys outstanding achievement award and has been named a distinguished fellow by the yale school of management public service during the nixonford periodedit this section of a biography of a living person 