ompany dominion midstream partners lp a delaware limited partnership formed by dominion resources inc to grow a portfolio of natural gas terminaling processing storage transportation and related assets and afiniti a worldwide company specializing in applied artificial intelligence solutions mr snow previously served on the boards of international consolidated airlines group sa nyse arca eu iag a multinational airline holding company from  until  and amerigroup corporation nyse agp a multistate managed health care company focused on managing publicly funded health care programs from  until  mr snow holds a ba from university of toledo a masters from the johns hopkins university a law degree from the george washington university and a phd in economics from the university of virginia based on his extensive experience with complex economic issues his service on the boards of multiple public companies and his exemplary record of leadership we have determined that mr snow should serve as a director source armada hoffler properties inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view john w snow phds full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like john w snow phd more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in john w snow phds network and community follow changes in john w snow phds employment and moneyinmotion connect with john w snow phd through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example john w snow phd john w snow phds connections  sign up now to view john w snow phds  connections » michael j ward board member ashland global holdings inc james g carlson former chairman president and chief executive officer amerigroup dennis h reilley board member marathon oil corporation john p surma board member marathon petroleum corporation richard c zoretic former executive vice president government business anthem inc gary r heminger chairman